{"tid":2391003,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[半山第一滴血]首殺入豪宅新盤 呎價近3萬西半山「63 POKFULAM」1座 入伙8個月就全民驗毒 2小時前","createTime":"2021-02-02T02:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T10:53:27.000Z","uid":239336,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"03380d3ca0bde136178521cfe48dfc7d0d00e50f","tid":2391003,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:43:08.000Z","msg":"佐敦有污水疫廈居民1周前被強制檢測，1周後大廈再爆確診，結果再要強制檢測，令人質疑措施只是擾民多於控疫。雖然過往強制檢測多屬舊樓，但隨着政府2月1日再降低驗毒門檻，即全港大廈只有1宗無源頭確診就要全棟驗毒後，強制檢測亦首次殺入豪宅，甚至是僅入伙半年多的貴價新盤。政府午夜刊憲，入伙僅8個月、呎價近3萬元的港島西半山納米豪宅新盤「63 POKFULAM」，1座居民要在4日或之前強制檢測。<br />\n<br />\n令全棟63 POKFULAM 1座（Amber House）居民都要驗毒的1宗無源頭確診，是本港第10466號個案。患者是28歲香港女子，1月26日發病，24日傳染期內（發病前2日起計）曾到灣仔盧押道扒房Feather &amp; Bone，除住址外，再無申報過去14日的其他行蹤。政府下令，1月19日至2月1日曾到訪63 POKFULAM 1座逾2小時者，須於2月4日或之前檢測。若已在1月30日至2月1日檢測者，可獲豁免。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210202/UGBBBLLTLFHV3JVB3MZLSXD4OE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2qqDrHfH2mDVuBtfaFaz9MH9tK5KaJduPKy6A0T6TPetni3NbLMKIubt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210202%2FUGBBBLLTLFHV3JVB3MZLSXD4OE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2qqDrHfH2mDVuBtfaFaz9MH9tK5KaJduPKy6A0T6TPetni3NbLMKIubt4&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=cd76c937\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210202%2FUGBBBLLTLFHV3JVB3MZLSXD4OE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2qqDrHfH2mDVuBtfaFaz9MH9tK5KaJduPKy6A0T6TPetni3NbLMKIubt4&h=1695943e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210202/UGBBBLLTLFHV3JVB3MZLSXD4OE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&